PN,41501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773765953
OL,3,CMeningitis B confirmed as strain
OL,4,Cbehind outbreak that has left two dead
OL,6,FSome cases of meningitis seen in Kent
OL,7,Fhave been confirmed as meningitis B,
OL,8,Fhealth officials have said, as
OL,9,Fhundreds of people are being urged to
OL,10,Fget antibiotics to stem the spread of
OL,11,Finfection.
OL,13,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA),
OL,14,Fwhich is investigating the outbreak
OL,15,Fthat left two young people dead and
OL,16,Fothers in hospital, said it would
OL,17,Fconfirm the strain seen in other cases
OL,18,F"when we have the full results".
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
