OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773765953
OL,3,CMeningitis B confirmed as strain
OL,4,Cbehind outbreak that has left two dead
OL,6,FThe majority of young people born
OL,7,Fbefore 2015 are not protected against
OL,8,Fmeningitis B unless they have had the
OL,9,Fjab privately. It was introduced on
OL,10,Fthe NHS for babies in 2015.
OL,12,FIt comes as hundreds of people who
OL,13,Fvisited Club Chemistry in Canterbury
OL,14,Fon March 5, 6 or 7 were told to come
OL,15,Fforward for preventative antibiotic
OL,16,Ftreatment as a "precautionary measure".
OL,26,@xD@POUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
