OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773765953
OL,3,CMeningitis B confirmed as strain
OL,4,Cbehind outbreak that has left two dead
OL,6,FThe UKHSA said on Monday evening that
OL,7,Fit was continuing to investigate the
OL,8,Foutbreak of meningitis, with 13 cases
OL,9,Fnotified since March 13, including two
OL,10,Fdeaths.
OL,12,FA Year 13 pupil in Faversham called
OL,13,FJuliette and a student at the
OL,14,FUniversity of Kent have died in the
OL,15,Foutbreak, with others treated in
OL,16,Fhospital. It is understood some people
OL,17,Fwere put in an induced coma.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773765953
OL,3,CMeningitis B confirmed as strain
OL,4,Cbehind outbreak that has left two dead
OL,6,FLouise Jones-Roberts, the owner of
OL,7,FClub Chemistry, said more than 2,000
OL,8,Fpeople would have visited the venue
OL,9,Fover the three dates.
OL,11,FThose who visited now need tracing for
OL,12,Fantibiotics.
OL,14,FMs Jones-Roberts said she believed
OL,15,Fmore than one case was connected to
OL,16,Fmingling at the club and she had "been
OL,17,Ftold they started showing symptoms on
OL,18,FMarch 10."
OL,26,@xD@bOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773765953
OL,3,CMeningitis B confirmed as strain
OL,4,Cbehind outbreak that has left two dead
OL,6,FMs Jones-Roberts said she had managed
OL,7,Fto contact around 90 out of 95 members
OL,8,Fof staff at the club and they had gone
OL,9,Fto get antibiotics.
OL,11,FShe added: "I'm devastated for the
OL,12,Ffamilies affected. It's so incredibly
OL,13,Fsad.
OL,15,F"I just really hope people know the
OL,16,Fsymptoms and no more lives are lost."
OL,18,FShe said the club would remain closed
OL,19,Funtil further notice, adding: "It is
OL,20,Fnot a hard decision to close ` we are
OL,21,Ftalking about people's lives."
OL,26,@sD@LOUwD@AOUxD@eO]{D@_OU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773765953
OL,3,CMeningitis B confirmed as strain
OL,4,Cbehind outbreak that has left two dead
OL,6,FMs Jones-Roberts later told the BBC
OL,7,Fthat a member of staff at the
OL,8,Fnightclub is one of the confirmed
OL,9,Fcases.
OL,11,FShe said: "He is in hospital, he is
OL,12,Fbeing treated and he's awaiting
OL,13,Ffurther tests to see if the treatment
OL,14,Fhe's had has improved his condition.
OL,16,F"We've got two other members of staff
OL,17,Fwho are currently in A&E with
OL,18,Fsuspected meningitis, and we're just
OL,19,Fwaiting for the update from them for
OL,20,Ftheir test results."
OL,26,@sD@KOUxD@AOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
