OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773765953
OL,3,CMeningitis B confirmed as strain
OL,4,Cbehind outbreak that has left two dead
OL,6,FTrish Mannes, UKHSA regional deputy
OL,7,Fdirector for the South East, said:
OL,8,F"Our investigations have identified
OL,9,Fthat some cases visited Club Chemistry
OL,10,Fin Canterbury and it is important that
OL,11,Fanyone who visited the club between
OL,12,FMarch 5 and March 7 now comes forward
OL,13,Ffor preventative antibiotic treatment
OL,14,Fas a precaution, as well as those
OL,15,Foffered antibiotics at the university
OL,16,F` these students are being contacted
OL,17,Fdirectly through the university."
OL,26,@pD@AOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
