OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773765953
OL,3,CMeningitis B confirmed as strain
OL,4,Cbehind outbreak that has left two dead
OL,6,FThe UKHSA has issued advice to 16,000
OL,7,Fstaff and students at the University
OL,8,Fof Kent, where antibiotics are also
OL,9,Fbeing offered to those who need them.
OL,11,FAmelia McIlroy, the headteacher of
OL,12,FQueen Elizabeth's Grammar School in
OL,13,FFaversham, confirmed one of its Year
OL,14,F13 pupils had died.
OL,16,FShe said: "Juliette embraced
OL,17,Feverything that school had to offer
OL,18,Fwith great enthusiasm and joy and her
OL,19,Fhumour and positivity were captivating.
OL,26,@xD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773765953
OL,3,CMeningitis B confirmed as strain
OL,4,Cbehind outbreak that has left two dead
OL,6,F"She was a genuinely caring and
OL,7,Fattentive listener, a true friend `
OL,8,Fwho listened with warmth, respect and
OL,9,Fsincere interest to her peers and to
OL,10,Four staff.
OL,12,F"In short, she was a lovely girl ` her
OL,13,Fbeautiful smile, her loving nature and
OL,14,Fher sense of fun will be hugely missed.
OL,16,F"We are all devastated."
OL,18,FJuliette's father told the BBC that
OL,19,Fthe family are "beyond devastated and
OL,20,Fthey have no words to express their
OL,21,Floss".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOUxD@XO]{D@POU}D@EO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
