FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773765953
OL,3,CMeningitis B confirmed as strain
OL,4,Cbehind outbreak that has left two dead
OL,6,FThe headmaster of Simon Langton
OL,7,FGrammar School for Boys said in a
OL,8,Fletter to parents that one of its Year
OL,9,F13 students has been admitted to
OL,10,Fhospital with meningitis.
OL,12,FAn update sent to parents at Norton
OL,13,FKnatchbull School in Ashford, Kent,
OL,14,Falso confirmed a diagnosis for a Year
OL,15,F13 student admitted to hospital.
OL,17,FA University of Kent spokesperson said
OL,18,Fon Monday it was taking advice from
OL,19,Fthe UKHSA and communicating with
OL,20,Fstudents and staff.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
