FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773765953
OL,3,CMeningitis B confirmed as strain
OL,4,Cbehind outbreak that has left two dead
OL,6,FIt said that there will be no in-
OL,7,Fperson assessments or exams for
OL,8,Fstudents this week.
OL,10,FThose who attended Club Chemistry can
OL,11,Fcollect antibiotics from: the Gate
OL,12,FClinic at Kent and Canterbury
OL,13,FHospital; Westgate Hall on Westgate
OL,14,FHall Road, Canterbury; the Carey
OL,15,FBuilding, Thanet Hub, Margate
OL,16,FNorthwood Road; and the Senate
OL,17,Fbuilding at the University of Kent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
